This category contains specific pages for various [[Avatars]]. It is not a comprehensive list.

Avatar pages should only be created for the following types of avatars:
* Official VRChat avatars
* Avatars part of the [[Public Avatars|Public Avatar Row]]
* Avatars otherwise featured by VRChat
* [[VRCWiki:Notability|Notable]] avatars made by the community

For a newly created Avatar page it should be obvious or made obvious that such Avatar or Avatar Type is notable enough. Therefore it is advised to create a [[VRCWiki:How to Contribute#Discussion Page|Discussion page]] right after a new Avatar page has been created with a note as for why the page was made. This helps to evaluate notability. Pages where this cannot be easily ascertained with may be deleted.

* Avatar Bases should have their own page and should include the [[Template:Infobox/AvatarType/doc|avatar type template infobox]]
** Avatars that are derivatives of an existing Avatar Base, should be listed as a Derivative Works on the page for that Avatar Base.
* Fully original Avatars should have their own page and should include the [[Template:Infobox/Avatar/doc|avatar template infobox]]
Avatars that were made by the Community (anyone other than VRChat itself) belong in the <code>Community:</code> namespace. Please add <code>Community:</code> in front of the page name for these. To learn more about namespaces, also see, [[VRCWiki:How_to_Contribute#Namespaces]] .